The fourth season of Business Tech’s latest online talk show, Business Talk, is coming soon. This season is sponsored by Discovery Business Insurance and will feature discussions with South African finance, business, and investment leaders. The show is hosted by radio and TV personality Michael Avery, who is well-known for being an anchor on Business Day TV and the Classic Business show on Classic FM. Discovery Business Insurance CEO Lana Ross and Discovery Life Deputy CEO Gareth Friedlander will be among those who join Avery on this season of Business Talk. These and other guests will discuss how consumers, employees, and businesses in their industries have been affected by the COVID-19 pandemic. The conversations will expand into each guest’s topics of expertise, providing rare insights from some of South Africa’s industry leaders. The series will be available on YouTube, Facebook, and the Business Talk website. The first three seasons of the show have been a big success, reaching over 750,000 views across all platforms in just eight months. Watch the trailer below and prepare for great insight from South Africa’s business leaders. 